{"tid":995833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有返過大陸既人今次有福啦！","createTime":"2019-01-25T18:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T12:58:57.000Z","uid":194415,"like":27,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c00454ab4161ee0a167344537d3cb037cf0152","tid":995833,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T18:29:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201901/18/P2019011800506.htm?fbclid=IwAR3YH_LY4stU4FIJ69zTAKuMeKcLdhIr1t-OXkOPZf0aumJ2gTFwFogKE44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F18%2FP2019011800506.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3YH_LY4stU4FIJ69zTAKuMeKcLdhIr1t-OXkOPZf0aumJ2gTFwFogKE44&d=iocUDTwEfCtZhjeG4z%2B5wwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=69cff143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201901/18/P2019011800506.htm?fbclid=IwAR3YH_LY4stU4FIJ69zTAKuMeKcLdhIr1t-OXkOPZf0aumJ2gTFwFogKE44</a><br />\n<br />\n香港特區與內地簽署相互認可和執行民商事判決的安排<br />\n<br />\n我估應該就係<br />\n只要大陸官司你輸（可能告緊你都未必知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n香港唔駛審，直接執行大陸法院判決<br />\n<br />\n翻過牆都可以追返黎告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你冇出席＞判輸要收監＞香港捉你係香港坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n洗頭艇都慳返！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603aaa64f827e6c54fc067534cbb07ea699fb2e9","tid":995833,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T18:38:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98b0a2392236d9e2fc0f9f53df0ae69ef2f6c6b6","tid":995833,"uid":154255,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T19:04:15.000Z","msg":"樓主表達能力滿分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32143f395ecf7d3f56a5a86e0cb5e43f73b646c2","tid":995833,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"大陸俾人呃爭人錢，黎香港都可以追債。<br />\n<